Company Description: Since Its Inception IN 1969, Wendy's Is One Of The Major Restaurants IN The World With More Than 6,600 Restaurants Around The Globe. A Member Of Arby's Group Inc., The Restaurant, Located IN Miami, Fla., Offers A Menu, Which Includes Burgers, Hamburgers, Salads, Beverages And Combos. Some Of The Special Items Available At Wendy's Are Old Fashioned Combos, Old Fashioned Hamburgers, Homestyle Chicken Go Wrap, Spicy Chicken Sandwich, Spicy Chicken Nuggets, Sweet & Spicy Asian Boneless Wings And Crispy Chicken Deluxe, To Name A Few. It Also Has Special Items For Kids, Such As Mandarin Oranges, Nesquik Low Fat Chocolate Milk And Sandwiches.

Wendy's Is A Chain Of More Than 6,500 Hamburger Restaurants IN North America And Other International Markets. Founded IN 1969, The Chain S Restaurants Serve A Variety Of Hamburgers Made With Grilled Beef And Vegetable Toppings. Its Restaurants Also Serve Garden Salads, Grilled Chicken Sandwiches And Baked Potatoes. The Chain S Restaurants  Side Dishes Include French Fries, Chocolate Chip Cookies, Chicken Nuggets And Yogurt. Its Restaurants Also Offer Wendy S Kids  Meal. Wendy's Operates Bakeries That Supply Sandwich Buns. The Chain Additionally Participates IN Various Community Activities, Such As Animal Welfare Programs, Educational Plans And Foster Care Adoption Schemes. Wendy's Is Owned And Operated By Wendy S International.

IN Operation Since 1969, Wendy's Is One Of The Leading Chains Of Fast-Food Service Restaurants IN The World. Located IN Miami, Fla., The Food-Service Firm Operates More Than 6,600 Restaurants Throughout The World. The Restaurant Serves A Number Of Food Items, Including Vegetarian Burgers, Hamburgers, Salads, Beverages, Desserts And Combos. Its Special Food Items Include Old-Fashioned Combos/Hamburgers, Spicy Chicken Sandwich/Nuggets And Crispy Chicken Deluxe. Wendy's Is A Part Of Arby's Group Inc., One Of The Largest Quick-Service Restaurant Companies IN The United States.

Wendy's International Is A Chain Of Restaurants That Operates And Franchises More Than 6,500 Wendy's Restaurants IN The United States And IN 21 Other Countries As Well As Territories. Located IN Miami, Fla., Its Menu Includes Garden Sensations Salads, Combo Choices, Super Value Menu, Frosty Shakes/Floats, Boneless Chicken Wings, Chicken Go Wraps And Signature Hamburger Offerings. The Company Is A Member Of Wendy's/Arby Group Inc., The Third Largest Quick Service Restaurant Company IN The United States That Comprises The Wendy's And Arby's Brands.
